# """
# DAG untuk sync data dari database kantor ke warehouse
# ==================================================

# Features:
# - Scheduled sync (setiap 1 jam)
# - Support full load dan incremental load
# - Direct psycopg2 connection (reliable untuk Airflow 3)
# - Automatic conflict resolution untuk incremental load
# - Foreign key aware (respects table dependencies)

# Data Flow:
# 1. Source: devom.silog.co.id (PostgreSQL - Office DB)
# 2. ETL: Airflow (extract, validate, load)
# 3. Target: postgres:5433/warehouse (Data Warehouse)
# 4. Visualization: Metabase dashboard

# Tables:
# - parent_armada, status_armada, jenis_armada (full load daily)
# - armada_tms (incremental: based on diubah_pada)
# - delivery_order (incremental: based on updated_at)

# Schedule:
# - Default: Every 1 hour (hourly sync)
# - Adjustable via cron expression
# """

